DWM(-plus) fork, with some patches, and lots of modified code.
Documentation later

Autostart goes in $HOME/.config/dwm/autostart

Debugging dual head setup:
   Xephyr :1 +xinerama -screen 600×400 &
   Xephyr :2 +xinerama -screen 600×400 &
   Xdmx :3 -display localhost:1 -display localhost:2 +xinerama

   Spawn on :3

Stable branch gets updated whenever, I've used master branch without no activity since few weeks
and works without any instability or usability bugs.
